    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PULSE//DEADLINE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The carnival was shut down.</strong><br><strong>It never closed.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From Deadlight Interactive, <i>PULSE//DEADLINE</i> is a 30-minute narrative horror experience set inside an abandoned carnival that slowly, deliberately begins to wake up around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a newly assigned night security guard. Your job is simple: monitor the grounds and report anything unusual.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At first, it’s just wind against loose metal.<br>Then the lights flicker on.<br>A carousel begins to turn.<br>Music plays from nowhere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And something starts moving between the attractions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210780/extras/6e494e3a9e05da30dbe44b17f35d93ab.poster.avif?t=1771527088\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210780/extras/6e494e3a9e05da30dbe44b17f35d93ab.webm?t=1771527088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210780/extras/6e494e3a9e05da30dbe44b17f35d93ab.mp4?t=1771527088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A CARNIVAL THAT COMES BACK TO LIFE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a decaying fairground where each ride tells part of a larger story — one of obsession, disappearance, and something that never left when the gates were locked.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The longer you stay, the more the environment changes. What begins as routine surveillance becomes a fight to understand what is happening — and how to escape it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210780/extras/7a638cda13751ccc458db1e295f45e4c.poster.avif?t=1771527088\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210780/extras/7a638cda13751ccc458db1e295f45e4c.webm?t=1771527088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210780/extras/7a638cda13751ccc458db1e295f45e4c.mp4?t=1771527088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OPTIONAL BIO-REACTIVE HORROR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>PULSE//DEADLINE</i> features optional heart-rate integration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a compatible device, the game can:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >React to spikes in your pulse</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intensify atmosphere and sound design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Subtly shift environmental behaviour</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjust tension pacing in real time</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No monitor required.<br>The full 30-minute experience is completely playable without biofeedback — integration simply deepens immersion for those who want it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210780/extras/eeae44090d41bb874d066c7dff0bbed5.poster.avif?t=1771527088\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210780/extras/eeae44090d41bb874d066c7dff0bbed5.webm?t=1771527088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210780/extras/eeae44090d41bb874d066c7dff0bbed5.mp4?t=1771527088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30-minute focused horror experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First-person immersive exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reactive environmental systems</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optional heart-rate integration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Psychological tension over cheap jumpscares</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streamer-friendly short-form format</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210780/extras/0fa02da639960ba190aa6659ae844229.poster.avif?t=1771527088\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210780/extras/0fa02da639960ba190aa6659ae844229.webm?t=1771527088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210780/extras/0fa02da639960ba190aa6659ae844229.mp4?t=1771527088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The rides are running. <br>The lights are on. <br>The gates are locked.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your shift ends at dawn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you make it that far...</p>",
